%% Export: docs/diagrams/01-cicd-flow.png
flowchart TB
  subgraph ci [CI - Azure DevOps]
    A[Push or manual run] --> B[Build Dockerfile]
    B --> C[Trivy scan]
    C --> D[Push to ACR dev]
    D --> E[Open GitHub PR]
    E --> F[Update image.digest in gitops/envs/dev]
  end

  subgraph gitops [GitOps]
    F --> G[Merge PR]
    G --> H[Argo CD sync dev]
    H --> I[Helm deploy to dev namespace]
  end

  subgraph promote [Promotion]
    J[Manual promote pipeline] --> K[az acr import by digest]
    K --> L[PR to gitops/envs/stage or prod]
    L --> M[Merge and Argo sync]
  end

  I --> J
